The paper deals with decision making under uncertainty, which is a core topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). It also introduces a new representation for functions over relational structures, which is relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and discrete mathematics (cs.DM). The paper also discusses reduction techniques, which are commonly used in programming languages (cs.PL) and databases (cs.DB).
